  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ab434477b46b60d499db11a05f19c820, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  centralAudio: {fileID: 1281537509}
  subtitlesText: {fileID: 194431416}
  useSubtitles: 1
  dialogues:
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: abdeced1a03761241b23abc809f0eb43, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="black">Office Phone:</color> *Phone Ringing*
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a3f78a7df925d204f8cc97ecf1999a02, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="red">Kaden:</color> Hello! It's you again. Congratulations
      on finishing your first overnight shift!
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5274be2743347134b8f8dba6c8680774, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="red">Kaden:</color> I'm guessing, as you're still here. you
      did not encounter said "intruder". But we've now figured out why he's trying
      to break in
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8e131ea5e0e99c74399b16351bcde52c, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="red">Kaden:</color> So we know he's after some files of an
      old project we did back in college. "Stanleys Speedrun". You might be familiar.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 587e28f9dd3391744adfa5c317b03038, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="red">Kaden:</color> If not. The contents of that file are
      extremely valuable and we can see why now he would want them back.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: b27936cb53729d04b9ed519a057b3eda, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="red">Finnix14:</color> You see he believes it was his work
      we completed in that project whilst he was our mentor in college.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8faac422b2f19ea4a9508938804c267e, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="red">Kaden:</color> all we ask, is that you make sure he does
      not find that file. We've even gone to the length of updating the Anti-Doug
      app to assist you from keeping him away. Good Luck Intern!
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  fireFinishEvent: 0
  finishedEvent:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  playOnAwake: 1
