--- !u!114 &1831322717
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1831322712}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ab434477b46b60d499db11a05f19c820, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  centralAudio: {fileID: 1831322715}
  subtitlesText: {fileID: 194431416}
  useSubtitles: 1
  dialogues:
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: abdeced1a03761241b23abc809f0eb43, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="black">Office Phone:</color> *Phone Ringing*
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3b789c9b6dc296d41b4aac48b121ba54, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> Hello? Hello, Hello? uhh you must
      be the new intern!
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1a0942c40d3a94d499888298f238374e, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> First overnight shift eh? ha! I remember
      when I did my first one of those.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a92ace946970dd049a9c9e6e4bcc49ad, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> I'm gonna cut to the chase. so, I've
      basically heard about a competitor attempting to break into the building recently.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 930ce8f00e614714a854f9a7249fcfea, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: '<color="green">Finnix14:</color> We have a rough idea as to who might
      it be, but we''re not certain as to why he might do it. '
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e9862b52144e2144792e3a2beda92b8b, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> Realistically you should be fine
      as this isn't the first time he has tried this. so we have prepared you with 
      a few tools to assist you.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6512b4ab5c21e9b4e8441c6c06f82c8b, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: '<color="green">Finnix14:</color> so, we think that he knows about
      our security systems, so if you are afraid hes in the building. Use the cameras
      on your pc. '
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5b67e44c0b582984a97856c3dbb2835d, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: '<color="green">Finnix14:</color> If you''re sure of it, your flashlight
      is your best tool to scare him off. '
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f17951af28f6b78449fc43952e401352, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> We also installed a new app on your
      pc. Which will allow you to play a sound signal at different parts in the building
      to lure him away from you.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e00809ca84a0b4649ba7b734ddab1476, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> That is a last resort application
      on your computer so use it wisely as it isnt quite finished yet.
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: aec4e5d3bb294e7459f80ec4f41f4d0b, type: 3}
    time: 0
    subtitles: <color="green">Finnix14:</color> anyways, aslong as you do what i've
      just told you. you should be safe. good luck intern!
    triggerEvent:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  fireFinishEvent: 0
  finishedEvent:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  playOnAwake: 1
